---
title: Japanese-Style Miso Sesame Noodles with Stir-Fried Cabbage, Carrots & Edamame
description: Celebrate Asian Heritage Month with a bowl of springy, chewy Sun Noodle Ramen Noodles! You’ll toss them in a savory-sweet sauce packed with flavor powerhouses like soy sauce, miso, sweet Thai chili sauce, and Korean chili flakes. Add in a colorful stir-fry of edamame, carrots, and red cabbage, and your one-bowl meal is ready (all in a quick 20 minutes!).
